---
title: Beef Tagliata with Herby Roasted Potatoes and Greens
description: We've upgraded the classic steak and potatoes dinner with a Northern Italian twist.  Juicy steak and herby potatoes all sit atop a luscious bed of slightly wilted greens. A final drizzle of dressing and you're set for a feast.
